title: Wisconsin Senate passes bill ending secret investigations
text: MADISON, Wis. (AP) - Republican legislators have nearly finished their drive to scale back secret John Doe investigations, moving within one vote of sending to Gov. Scott Walker a bill barring prosecutors from using the process to probe political misconduct. The proposal comes after prosecutors used the John Doe procedure ... ...
